parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially at low speeds when the vehicle is in a confined space, such as a parking lot or garage.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates even when the accelerator pedal is not being depressed
the vehicle accelerates while the brake pedal is being pressed
the vehicle hesitates or lunges forward when rolling to a stop
the vehicle accelerates intermittently while entering a highway or making a turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the AFS can cause the headlights to malfunction, resulting in reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: Headlights shine directly at the ground
limited illumination of the highway ahead
AFS warning light illuminated on the instrumental panel
reduced visibility at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the height control sensor can cause the headlights to malfunction, resulting in reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: Headlights not angled straight
limited illumination of the highway ahead
reduced visibility at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The glare from HID headlights can cause temporary loss of vision, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: Glare from HID headlights
temporary loss of vision
reduced visibility at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
side curtain airbag does not deploy in a broadside collision
no airbag deployment in a severe accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden acceleration while parking
inability to stop the vehicle
racing engine
vehicle moves in an unintended direction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning airbag sensor can lead to improper airbag deployment, increasing the risk of injury or fatality to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: Airbag on/off switch malfunctions
airbag turns off permanently
"take to dealer" light illuminates.
